WEBVTT

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:03.669
Hey, good morning family! We are

00:00:03.679 --> 00:00:06.110
excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:06.120 --> 00:00:07.590
Boy, we have some stuff to talk to

00:00:07.590 --> 00:00:07.600
you

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:10.390
about. We're excited. We'll

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:11.990
get to the prayer in a minute, but we

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.749
have some amazing news to talk

00:00:14.759 --> 00:00:17.790
about what the Lord is doing.

00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:20.230
We went to a healing service again

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:23.589
tonight, and the Shekinah of Glory was

00:00:23.599 --> 00:00:25.669
there. I'm telling you

00:00:25.679 --> 00:00:28.310
all, you know there's people

00:00:28.310 --> 00:00:28.320
who

00:00:28.320 --> 00:00:30.070
say, 'Well, we don't have time to drive to

00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:32.709
go to a certain service or be a part of

00:00:32.719 --> 00:00:35.830
a revival.'How desperate, how hungry are

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:38.069
you? I'm not criticizing you; I'm trying

00:00:38.079 --> 00:00:41.069
to say, folks, it's time to get hungry. The

00:00:41.079 --> 00:00:45.110
King is coming! The King is coming!

00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:48.189
In this little town of

00:00:48.189 --> 00:00:48.199
Eufaula,

00:00:48.199 --> 00:00:51.470
Oklahoma, the glory at the

00:00:51.480 --> 00:00:53.549
Lighthouse Church is—is it the Lighthouse

00:00:53.559 --> 00:00:54.950
Church? Yeah, I think that's what it's

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:56.709
called. Precious people there at this

00:00:56.719 --> 00:00:59.470
church, precious men and women of God. The

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:01.470
pastors there, the associate pastor

00:01:01.480 --> 00:01:03.750
and the main pastor, are amazing

00:01:03.750 --> 00:01:03.760
people—really,

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:06.270
really awesome men and

00:01:06.280 --> 00:01:08.270
women of God. And

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:09.990
the daughter-in-law, she sings like a

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:12.190
bird, man. She could bring down the

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:14.149
glory with her voice, and it

00:01:14.149 --> 00:01:14.159
was

00:01:14.159 --> 00:01:18.830
amazing. But they have Billy Burke

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:21.630
there, and I'm going to do this

00:01:21.630 --> 00:01:21.640
without

00:01:21.640 --> 00:01:25.749
crying, but I'm going to tell you all

00:01:25.759 --> 00:01:29.149
this: two nights in a row, I've gotten a

00:01:29.159 --> 00:01:31.109
touch from the Lord that will

00:01:31.119 --> 00:01:34.270
forever change us

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:37.550
both. I would encourage you, if

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:39.950
Billy Burke is ever in your

00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:42.310
area, wherever you live, if you look at

00:01:42.320 --> 00:01:43.109
his

00:01:43.119 --> 00:01:46.190
itinerary, just try to go to at

00:01:46.200 --> 00:01:47.950
least one or two of his meetings and

00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:51.469
bless him. Bless him when you go;

00:01:51.479 --> 00:01:56.910
he is good ground.

00:01:56.920 --> 00:02:00.069
I believe with all my

00:02:00.069 --> 00:02:00.079
heart—like

00:02:00.079 --> 00:02:02.590
Diana, I wish I could give more

00:02:02.600 --> 00:02:05.550
because when you

00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:08.790
see people's lives being changed by the

00:02:08.790 --> 00:02:08.800
glory—people

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:11.630
that are broken,

00:02:11.640 --> 00:02:14.910
suicidal, and just ready to give

00:02:14.920 --> 00:02:16.869
up on life—and you see the presence of

00:02:16.879 --> 00:02:21.509
God change them.

00:02:21.519 --> 00:02:23.509
You see their countenance when

00:02:23.519 --> 00:02:25.070
they come up

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:27.550
there so heavy and burdened down,

00:02:27.560 --> 00:02:30.990
just ready to give up,

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:32.309
and then when the power of God knocks them

00:02:32.319 --> 00:02:33.910
down and they get up, their

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:36.670
face looks different. The demonic spirits

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:39.589
lifted off of them. So many people

00:02:39.599 --> 00:02:42.630
we have seen in the last two days have a

00:02:42.640 --> 00:02:45.470
radical visitation from the

00:02:45.480 --> 00:02:49.190
Lord. Tonight, after last night, I

00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:50.990
felt like I was being a pig

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:53.070
because I got a touch last night.

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:55.190
Diana said, because we have our own needs,

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:56.630
we went up and had Megan

00:02:56.640 --> 00:02:59.350
prayed for, but we didn't talk about

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:01.509
the stuff that we were believing

00:03:01.509 --> 00:03:01.519
for.

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:04.630
So Diana said, 'Brandon, why don't we

00:03:04.640 --> 00:03:06.830
go down to the front?'and I said, 'Well,

00:03:06.830 --> 00:03:06.840
shouldn't we

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:08.309
let all the

00:03:08.319 --> 00:03:10.070
other people get ministered to?'But the

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:15.589
Lord said, 'Go. It's okay to be greedy

00:03:15.599 --> 00:03:17.390
when it comes to

00:03:17.390 --> 00:03:17.400
My presence.'I'm

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:20.509
hungry,

00:03:20.519 --> 00:03:22.589
and when you hunger and thirst

00:03:22.599 --> 00:03:25.430
after righteousness, He said He'd

00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:25.440
fill you.

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:27.309
I told her, 'Come on, babe,'so I

00:03:27.319 --> 00:03:28.949
grabbed her hand and we ran up to the

00:03:28.959 --> 00:03:31.229
front. Bren watched Megan and

00:03:31.239 --> 00:03:33.110
made sure she was okay while we went up

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:35.750
there and got prayed for. The

00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:38.229
moment we hit the line—we were at the

00:03:38.239 --> 00:03:40.869
back of the

00:03:40.869 --> 00:03:40.879
line—it

00:03:40.879 --> 00:03:43.149
doesn't matter where you are in the line;

00:03:43.159 --> 00:03:45.910
He meets you where you are. You don't

00:03:45.920 --> 00:03:48.070
have to wait. You

00:03:48.080 --> 00:03:49.710
don't even have to have hands laid on

00:03:49.720 --> 00:03:52.509
you; He meets you

00:03:52.519 --> 00:03:54.869
where your faith is. We got up and it

00:03:54.879 --> 00:03:56.830
was almost over, and we

00:03:56.840 --> 00:03:59.030
thought that he was closing. We were

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:00.509
like, 'You know, we're

00:04:00.519 --> 00:04:02.069
just going to go.'So we went down there,

00:04:02.079 --> 00:04:03.149
and we were at the back of the line at

00:04:03.159 --> 00:04:06.509
the very end of the service, and the

00:04:06.519 --> 00:04:08.149
tangible presence of God hit us so

00:04:08.159 --> 00:04:11.630
strong.

00:04:11.640 --> 00:04:14.069
I could barely stand up. The glory

00:04:14.079 --> 00:04:15.630
was all over my legs so much that they

00:04:15.640 --> 00:04:18.509
were wobbly, and I felt like I was

00:04:18.519 --> 00:04:21.670
so intoxicated with the Holy Spirit that

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:23.510
I was wanting to lean against a

00:04:23.520 --> 00:04:26.189
wall. The closer we got to the front

00:04:26.199 --> 00:04:28.749
of the altar, the presence of the

00:04:28.749 --> 00:04:28.759
Lord—I

00:04:28.759 --> 00:04:30.510
started

00:04:30.510 --> 00:04:30.520
sweating.

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:32.270
She couldn't stand; I had to

00:04:32.280 --> 00:04:33.710
hold her up with my shoulder. She was

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:35.390
holding on to me so she wouldn't fall

00:04:35.400 --> 00:04:38.310
out, and I was bracing myself.

00:04:38.320 --> 00:04:41.590
All of a sudden, when we got to

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:43.749
him and he said, 'What is wrong?'and he

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:46.590
prayed for us, the glory of the Lord hit

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:49.830
me so strong. He said, 'It's the Shekinah of

00:04:49.840 --> 00:04:51.909
Glory on y'all,'and he said,

00:04:51.919 --> 00:04:54.350
'Watch me.'He touched me—bam!—and I hit

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:55.830
the ground. I'm telling you, when I

00:04:55.840 --> 00:04:58.350
did, I felt the presence of the Lord just

00:04:58.360 --> 00:05:02.310
hit me like a wave, and it hit Diana.

00:05:02.320 --> 00:05:04.909
Oh, I've never felt it that strong in my

00:05:04.919 --> 00:05:09.590
entire life! I was just weeping,

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:11.390
'Thank You,

00:05:11.390 --> 00:05:11.400
Jesus.'But

00:05:11.400 --> 00:05:15.070
this is the part... we're

00:05:15.080 --> 00:05:17.710
going to rewind a little bit here. I went

00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:20.670
to the store today to get her some

00:05:20.680 --> 00:05:23.390
coats and stuff for the winter so

00:05:23.400 --> 00:05:25.110
that we'd have some nice clothes for her

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:26.870
to wear on these videos and when we

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:28.309
go out to these meetings that the Lord's

00:05:28.319 --> 00:05:30.629
telling us to go to.

00:05:30.639 --> 00:05:32.390
I said, 'Hey babe, you asked for

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:34.270
some perfume,

00:05:34.280 --> 00:05:35.950
let me go ahead

00:05:35.950 --> 00:05:35.960
and

00:05:35.960 --> 00:05:38.430
buy you

00:05:38.430 --> 00:05:38.440
some.'I'm

00:05:38.440 --> 00:05:40.270
glad you like it because

00:05:40.280 --> 00:05:42.909
it was a treat. So I got her this

00:05:42.919 --> 00:05:45.309
bottle of perfume, and she said, 'Man,

00:05:45.319 --> 00:05:47.710
Brandon, it smells so lovely. I love this.

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:49.390
This is really

00:05:49.390 --> 00:05:49.400
nice.'I

00:05:49.400 --> 00:05:52.070
surprised her, and then what did the Lord

00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:55.070
say to you? What did you say? Well, I

00:05:55.080 --> 00:05:57.670
was thinking whenever we were driving

00:05:57.680 --> 00:06:00.309
in the car,

00:06:00.319 --> 00:06:03.629
I was thinking about how last night I

00:06:03.639 --> 00:06:06.629
had had a visitation from the

00:06:06.639 --> 00:06:09.990
Lord. I

00:06:09.990 --> 00:06:10.000
smelled

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:12.550
a campfire when I was just folding

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:15.710
laundry. We were listening

00:06:15.710 --> 00:06:15.720
to

00:06:15.720 --> 00:06:17.230
'Fire, Fire, Shut Up in My Bones.'I was

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:20.189
listening to that on the TV; I

00:06:20.199 --> 00:06:22.830
had the Autumn Assembly of Prayer on our TV

00:06:22.840 --> 00:06:25.469
from

00:06:25.479 --> 00:06:27.029
years ago. They were praying

00:06:27.039 --> 00:06:29.309
'Fire, fire, fire shut up in my

00:06:29.309 --> 00:06:29.319
bones!'Lynn

00:06:29.319 --> 00:06:32.510
Hammond was preaching,

00:06:32.510 --> 00:06:32.520
and

00:06:32.520 --> 00:06:36.390
I was just folding laundry, but I was

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:39.110
sucked into it. I was listening and soaking it in, and it was

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:41.629
like

00:06:41.639 --> 00:06:43.230
I was there. I forgot I was

00:06:43.240 --> 00:06:45.469
even folding laundry; I was just doing it

00:06:45.479 --> 00:06:47.390
robotically. All of a sudden, I

00:06:47.400 --> 00:06:50.309
smelled a campfire. I asked

00:06:50.319 --> 00:06:53.629
Bren, 'Do you smell that?'and he

00:06:53.639 --> 00:06:56.230
goes, 'No, Mom, I don't smell

00:06:56.230 --> 00:06:56.240
anything.'I

00:06:56.240 --> 00:07:00.029
said, 'It is so strong.

00:07:00.039 --> 00:07:02.390
Is there a fire going on in

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:03.830
this house?'We looked around,

00:07:03.840 --> 00:07:06.390
and I said, 'It's just right

00:07:06.390 --> 00:07:06.400
here.'We

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:08.550
found out that it was just

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:11.350
right where I was standing

00:07:11.350 --> 00:07:11.360
that

00:07:11.360 --> 00:07:13.550
I smelled it.

00:07:16.919 --> 00:07:19.270
Bren came and stood

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:20.909
right by me, and he's like, 'Mom, I don't

00:07:20.919 --> 00:07:23.990
smell anything.'I said, 'It's

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:26.790
the Holy Spirit.

00:07:26.800 --> 00:07:30.189
I feel His presence

00:07:30.199 --> 00:07:31.710
here.'So,

00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:35.629
all of a sudden, I just felt

00:07:35.639 --> 00:07:39.189
His presence on me, and I just hit

00:07:39.199 --> 00:07:42.790
the floor. I was just on my face

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:45.710
before God in intercessory prayer,

00:07:45.710 --> 00:07:45.720
just

00:07:45.720 --> 00:07:47.830
travailing and

00:07:47.840 --> 00:07:51.629
travailing. After it was over, I

00:07:51.639 --> 00:07:53.270
went back to where the laundry was

00:07:53.280 --> 00:07:54.270
and

00:07:54.280 --> 00:07:56.309
I picked up the laundry

00:07:56.319 --> 00:08:00.710
and smelled it. Bren goes,

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:02.350
'No, the clothes don't smell.'I said,

00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:03.990
'I know the clothes don't smell

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:05.430
because I just got them out of the

00:08:05.440 --> 00:08:07.550
dryer,'but

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:09.309
I've

00:08:09.319 --> 00:08:12.589
never been

00:08:12.599 --> 00:08:15.469
around a campfire where it doesn't

00:08:15.479 --> 00:08:18.029
permeate the clothes. I just wanted

00:08:18.039 --> 00:08:20.550
to see if His presence

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:23.629
permeated those clothes, but

00:08:23.629 --> 00:08:23.639
they

00:08:23.639 --> 00:08:25.110
didn't smell

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:28.430
like anything. So I

00:08:28.440 --> 00:08:30.270
forgot about it, and the next day he gave

00:08:30.280 --> 00:08:32.709
me the perfume.

00:08:32.719 --> 00:08:34.909
We were driving down there,

00:08:34.919 --> 00:08:36.389
and I was just looking out the

00:08:36.399 --> 00:08:39.630
window, talking to God in my

00:08:39.630 --> 00:08:39.640
heart.

00:08:42.029 --> 00:08:42.039
I

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:44.910
said,

00:08:44.920 --> 00:08:46.949
'Oh, I like my perfume,

00:08:46.959 --> 00:08:48.990
Lord.'I

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:50.829
saw all the

00:08:50.839 --> 00:08:52.550
flowers outside and said, 'They're so

00:08:52.560 --> 00:08:56.190
beautiful, Lord. I love the way flowers

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:59.110
smell.'Then

00:08:59.120 --> 00:09:01.990
I was also thinking about

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.870
fragrances in general, and I was thinking

00:09:03.880 --> 00:09:06.590
about last night.

00:09:06.600 --> 00:09:10.110
I was thinking about

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:12.470
when his

00:09:12.470 --> 00:09:12.480
it

00:09:12.480 --> 00:09:16.190
passed. When he first passed,

00:09:16.200 --> 00:09:18.750
his grandma would take his clothes and

00:09:18.760 --> 00:09:20.710
she would

00:09:20.710 --> 00:09:20.720
breathe

00:09:20.720 --> 00:09:22.350
them

00:09:22.360 --> 00:09:23.990
in because she wanted to smell it

00:09:23.990 --> 00:09:24.000
because

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:26.829
she missed him so much.

00:09:26.839 --> 00:09:30.269
I remember

00:09:30.279 --> 00:09:32.949
when she said,

00:09:32.959 --> 00:09:36.230
'His fragrance is even leaving

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:38.870
the clothes.'After a

00:09:38.870 --> 00:09:38.880
couple of

00:09:38.880 --> 00:09:40.949
weeks, his

00:09:40.949 --> 00:09:40.959
scent

00:09:40.959 --> 00:09:45.150
started wearing off

00:09:51.920 --> 00:09:54.110
his old clothes, and

00:09:54.120 --> 00:09:56.670
she

00:09:56.680 --> 00:09:59.630
was

00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:01.470
crying.

00:10:01.480 --> 00:10:05.910
I heard

00:10:05.920 --> 00:10:08.470
the Lord say to me,

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:10.389
'Diana,'because

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:11.550
I was thinking about those

00:10:11.560 --> 00:10:13.190
clothes and I wondered why they

00:10:13.200 --> 00:10:16.670
didn't smell like that.

00:10:16.680 --> 00:10:19.949
It was so tangible, Lord.

00:10:19.959 --> 00:10:22.190
And He said,

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:25.110
'Diana, the fragrances don't last very

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:27.710
long because when you

00:10:27.720 --> 00:10:29.829
take a flower and put

00:10:29.829 --> 00:10:29.839
it

00:10:29.839 --> 00:10:32.590
in a vase, even the

00:10:32.600 --> 00:10:34.550
fragrance from a rose dies.

00:10:34.560 --> 00:10:36.990
It doesn't smell very

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:38.949
good forever

00:10:38.959 --> 00:10:41.389
because it's separated from its

00:10:41.389 --> 00:10:41.399
source.'It

00:10:41.399 --> 00:10:44.949
hit me,

00:10:44.959 --> 00:10:48.470
and He said,

00:10:48.480 --> 00:10:51.629
'Diana,

00:10:51.639 --> 00:10:55.030
I smell so good. My

00:10:55.040 --> 00:10:57.590
fragrance is

00:10:57.590 --> 00:10:57.600
amazing.'I

00:10:57.600 --> 00:11:00.509
said, 'Oh, Father, I bet

00:11:00.509 --> 00:11:00.519
it

00:11:00.519 --> 00:11:03.829
is.'Then

00:11:03.839 --> 00:11:06.750
when we got there in

00:11:06.760 --> 00:11:09.430
that line, at the back of the

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:11.790
line,

00:11:11.800 --> 00:11:17.350
I started smelling this

00:11:17.360 --> 00:11:20.629
fragrance. It was the most beautiful

00:11:20.639 --> 00:11:25.829
fragrance I've ever

00:11:25.839 --> 00:11:28.230
smelled.

00:11:34.160 --> 00:11:37.269
When you

00:11:37.279 --> 00:11:40.350
breathed it in, it was like

00:11:40.360 --> 00:11:43.509
life.

00:11:43.519 --> 00:11:46.389
I felt

00:11:46.399 --> 00:11:48.710
the Holy Spirit

00:11:48.710 --> 00:11:48.720
say,

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:52.470
'Breathe.'The

00:11:52.480 --> 00:11:55.710
more

00:11:55.710 --> 00:11:55.720
I

00:11:55.720 --> 00:11:58.790
breathed,

00:11:58.800 --> 00:12:01.190
the more I could hardly

00:12:01.200 --> 00:12:04.069
stand.

00:12:04.079 --> 00:12:07.389
I

00:12:07.399 --> 00:12:12.389
was like, 'Guys, Heaven's going to smell so

00:12:12.389 --> 00:12:12.399
good!'I

00:12:12.399 --> 00:12:16.189
was standing next to her, and

00:12:16.199 --> 00:12:19.069
she said, 'Brandon, do you not smell

